data.description:
This gorgeous two-story home with four bedrooms and three full bathrooms is a perfect find for you. Step into the welcoming entryway, leading to a lengthy foyer, passing the stairs to reveal an inviting living space. Adjacent to this area is an open kitchen and dining space, ideal for meal prep, and quality time around the generous kitchen island. Tucked, conveniently behind the stairs is a laundry room. The primary suite and another bedroom reside on the first floor, while two secondary bedrooms, and an additional living area, occupy the upper level. Enjoy serene evenings on the patio, taking in the view of the spacious backyard, or take leisurely stroll through the peaceful neighborhood. Conveniently, located to restaurants, shopping and more.

Renter pays all utilities plus yard care. Pets allowed, maximum of two up to 65 pounds. Pet fee is a nonrefundable $500. No smoking, no subleases.
